                        <interp inst="t18791124-65-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was also charged with having been convicted at Clerkenwell in November</hi>, 1876, <hi rend="italic">in the name of Wood, of stealing from the person, to, which he</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.**†—<hi rend="italic">
